original: Zetterström, Tor Helge, arkitekt, Göteborg, f. 17/7/84 i Gbg av C. J. Z. o Maria Andersson. G. m. Ingrid Pettersson. Barn: Rolf Ragnar f. 30. — CTI, Polytechn. Strehtz, Tyskl, 04. Egen verks. s. arkit. o. byggm. i Gbg sed. 12. Medl. av SAR, Tekn. samf. i Gbg o. Byggn:tekn. fören.
translated: Zetterström, Tor Helge, architect, Gothenburg, b. 17/7/84 in Gothenburg, son of C. J. Z. and Maria Andersson. Married to Ingrid Pettersson in the year 19xx. Children: Rolf Ragnar b. 30. — CTI, Polytechn. Strehtz, Germany, 04. Working as an architect and contractor in Gothenburg since 12. Member of SAR, Technical Society in Gothenburg, and Building Technology Association.
